::Cledar::

Cledar ducks, sending Sinnertwin flying over him and the pods
following the Decepticon, releasing their vines all over Sinnertwin
(if you agree, Jer), and tightening them around him.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., robertdahl <rdahl@t...> wrote:
> The slash of Cledar did little more than knock one of the heads to
the
> side. Sinnertwin was moving in for the kill now. Little did he know
that
> the pods were coming at him. They burst behind him, and sent him
forward
> onto Cledar. He lashed out with one head at Cledar, as the other
looked
> behind him at his charred back armour.
